gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Jazz 105, Pelicans 100
gameRecap.excerpt: The Jazz defeated the Pelicans, 105-100. Collin Sexton recorded a team-high 16 points for the Jazz, while Keyonte George added 15 points, six rebounds, and five assists in the victory. Brandon Ingram (26 points, six rebounds, eight assists) and Jordan Hawkins (25 points, six rebounds) combined for 51 points for the Pelicans in the losing effort. The Jazz improve to 5-11 on the season, while the Pelicans fall to 9-8.
